@Mojo(name="aot-sample-config", defaultPhase=PACKAGE, requiresDependencyResolution=COMPILE_PLUS_RUNTIME) public class AotSampleMojo extends AbstractMicronautAotCliMojo
Generates a sample aot.properties showcasing all the possible values along with a description.
